column1: /*REMARK1: Make sure longer regex's preceed shorter ones which overlap.
/*REMARK2: Regex are treated alphabetically, and regex who are treated later overwrite earlier ones. So when 'zxxx' and 'axxx' overlap, 'zxxx' will overwrite 'axxx'.
/*#14-nl: replaced all '.*' by '[а-я-]+' at the beginning of regex for endings, to improve performance -> #15-nl replaced by '[а-я-0-9]{2,}'
